- Document Resource Governor classifier function logic for review
- Ensure classification doesn't grant elevated context/permissions
- Include Resource Governor configuration in change management
- Periodically review configuration as part of security audits

**97. How do you handle an audit request to demonstrate "separation between production and non-production" data and access?**
- Maintain clearly separate environments (network, credentials, instances)
- Ensure non-prod doesn't contain unmasked production data (see Q47)
- Show distinct access lists for prod vs. non-prod with different approval owners
