## E. Primary Technical SME for Database Controls During Audits
*(Resume: "Acted as primary technical SME for database controls during audits")*

**28. As the SME, how do you prepare before an audit kickoff meeting?**
- Review prior audit findings and current remediation status
- Pre-stage the standard evidence package for in-scope systems
