**49. How do you tie encryption controls back to specific compliance requirements when an auditor asks "why this control"?**
- Maintain a control-to-requirement mapping (e.g., TDE → encryption-at-rest requirement under [framework])
- For each encryption control, document which regulation/policy clause it satisfies
- This allows you to answer "why" directly rather than just "what we do"
